Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 沈睡心底的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 向充滿希望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}無論倒下多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要再次站立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:42.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待 奇跡豈會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越吧 昨日懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:52.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握住 浮於銀河的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}不要屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馳騁的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}向著夢想之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:07.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著這天馬的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:12.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 熾熱燃燒的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信決不屈服的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:26.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 決不停滯決不放棄的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.76,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}直指Ω　奮勇戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.33,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣&galaxy字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當世間面臨邪惡之神的侵略時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便必定會出現奮起迎戰的戰士 聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年輕聖鬥士們嶄新的傳說即將展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙等人在第六宮處女宮成功會合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 守護處女宮的處女座Virgo的不動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有著在黃金聖鬥士中也數一數二的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正當年輕的聖鬥士們耗盡力量之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯的兒子伊甸出現在了他們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距地球被黑暗所籠罩還有7小時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…頭髮的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 為何至此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是收拾青銅聖鬥士的話 吾一人足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本無法使我移動分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以我才來此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為與你一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的反叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 決心的鬥志！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人要打倒瑪爾斯 而你要與他們同流合污嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只為通過此處而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瑪爾斯之子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該可以在這十二宮中自由走動的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對父親來說 我已經成為了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的理想十分崇高 但實現方式卻是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我決心要讓父親清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 在守護父親的聖鬥士中 被譽為擁有最強小宇宙的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我必須要打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前又倍增了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的小宇宙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 瑪爾斯之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是想要阻礙這個世界的淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你 也不可以邁過這處女宮半步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明王來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動的攻擊被破解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷光火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 竟輕易破解了我的五大明王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的攻擊對我完全不疼不癢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法令我移動分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識相些 速速退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要通過這裡 前往父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸的攻擊奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸行斷罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瑪爾斯的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可因一時衝動而莽撞行事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且冷靜一下頭腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要助伊甸一臂之力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖只有一瞬間…但你竟能令我移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來並非僅僅出於對父親的憎恨與憤怒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚有其他的原因 驅使你前進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟所為何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悔恨 不動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西亦能化作力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 一直以來認為自己是絕對正確 引導著世界走入正軌的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看來為了回應你的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也應前往更高的層次才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更高的層次？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.75,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指自性輪身、正法輪身、教令輪身三者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身具三身 稱為三輪身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:04.26,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教令輪身（きょうりょうりんしん）：大日如來為教化剛強難度的眾生，現大忿怒相以降伏之。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一為借暴力阻止忤逆者的恐怖之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.66,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正法輪身（しょうぼうりんしん）：大日如來垂跡現菩薩身，以正法化益眾生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一為靜靜教誨宇宙真理之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:14.54,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自性輪身（じしょうりんしん）：曼荼羅中台大日如來以本地自性的佛體化益眾生， 因此稱為自性輪身。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一身乃 化自身為頓悟之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已無需戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸於我的世界中 平靜地離去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔和的風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水聲潺潺入耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的烈焰好像漸漸平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離去…那種事我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動 我會繼續戰鬥 直到你讓路為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實乃一眾可憐之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼見如此純潔清澈之世 仍執意言戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心不會平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至完成阿莉雅的願望之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動 你不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了願意傾盡生命守護之人的世界 是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？那是怎樣的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是絕望的世界 痛失光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明可以阻止瑪爾斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻只是眼睜睜地看著 什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 想讓你老爹醒悟也為時已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠如所言 我什麼也做不到 什麼也沒去做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今唯有這份悔恨在激勵我前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無意與你們並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 少礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人是很礙事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使他們離開這裡 無法打敗我的人亦無法前行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾便於此 為汝忤逆親父之罪行 施予斷罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸只是為一時感情困擾而陷入迷亂 您不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人的偉志 自他幼時起我便令其耳濡目染
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應當已經充分理解了自身的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸呢 不管他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不想和我們並肩戰鬥 還把我們趕出了處女宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是打倒瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就把不動交給伊甸 繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 伊甸救了我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那傢伙畢竟是瑪爾斯的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青銅聖鬥士們突破了處女宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青銅聖鬥士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距瑪爾斯大人夙願得償僅一步之遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候送那些礙事之人回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就穿起這件聖衣 將他們送向時間的盡頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 這就是你所渴求的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖鬥士？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開自己的宮殿了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙本應該是時鐘座的白銀聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是執掌時間與永恆的水瓶座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarius的黃金聖鬥士 時貞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害大哥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為黃金聖鬥士了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡邂逅過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都不會再向上一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰阻攔 我們都要去上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然臉和以前一樣 但總覺得哪裡不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有些不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙剛一消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個瞬間就被揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的速度已經快到肉眼無法看到的程度了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥 戰鬥吧 時貞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息在流動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼移動得那麼慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間拳 3秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那傢伙的速度快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我們變慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間的流動發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 可以操縱時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以做到那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就用比時間還快的光速來擊中他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你攻擊到我需要8秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此游刃有餘的狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 簡直沒法戰鬥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這股力量太異常了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像被聖衣上浮現出的那骷髏命令似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物皆為時間之奴僕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對生物來說 最難對付的對手就是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 自我獲得這件聖衣時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便是最強的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是聖鬥士 無人不希望自己能身披這水瓶座黃金聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你穿也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上這件聖衣 你就能最大限度地發揮力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括駕馭時間的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為這件聖衣的奴僕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴僕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件聖衣有強烈的自我意識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被聖衣的自我承認之前 你要做它的奴僕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 只要能夠獲得駕馭時間的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始你就是水瓶座的黃金聖鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守聖衣的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是水瓶座的黃金聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將對這件聖衣言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼能被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡放棄的話就沒有未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間在繼續流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們幾個的時間就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此處乃審判之間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身為瑪爾斯之子 前途似錦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何卻要忤逆親父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到父親身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑借自己的雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑借自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來唇舌之力已不能令你動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菩提證悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己應做之事 相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並一心一意勇往直前的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 少年們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍有站起來的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你力量的源泉究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所祈願的世界的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我力量的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他覺醒了第七感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝曾言要讓瑪爾斯醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便醒悟 又有何用？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造一個沒有戰爭且美麗平靜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親想用力量重置這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該建立在現存的生命的犧牲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菩提證悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這招來結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶慟滅（Orion's Devastation)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行人再次見到了天秤座玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善惡分明的天秤座聖鬥士玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行動和之前黃金聖鬥士大相逕庭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時貞與玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高階聖鬥士間的禁忌之戰即將拉開帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤宮的再會！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激突、黃金對黃金！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
